OL,3,CMore than 30 families say Swansea
OL,4,Cmaternity services review 'has no
OL,5,Ccredibility'
OL,7,FMore than 30 families concerned about
OL,8,Fmaternity services at a hospital in
OL,9,FSwansea have written to the chair of a
OL,10,Freview into standards there calling
OL,11,Ffor it to be scrapped.
OL,13,FSwansea Bay University Health Board
OL,14,Fannounced in December that a review
OL,15,Finto Singleton Hospital was needed "in
OL,16,Forder to maintain the public
OL,17,Fconfidence in the care being
OL,18,Fdelivered."
