OL,4,Cmaternity services review 'has no
OL,5,Ccredibility'
OL,7,FIt followed an ITV Wales This Week
OL,8,Finvestigation which found critical
OL,9,Fissues within the maternity unit and a
OL,10,FHealthcare Inspectorate Wales report
OL,11,Fwhich found the unit to be "unsafe".
OL,13,FFollowing these reports the Welsh
OL,14,FGovernment announced it was placing
OL,15,Fthe service under enhanced monitoring.
