OL,7,FThe most recent Healthcare
OL,8,FInspectorate Wales (HIW) report in
OL,9,FJuly found there are still a number of
OL,10,Fproblems on the unit, including with
OL,11,Fthe number of staff in the antenatal
OL,12,Fassessment unit.
OL,14,FIn a letter to the health board this
OL,15,Fweek, the Swansea Bay Maternity
OL,16,FSupport Group said: "Over the past
OL,17,Feight months we have been growing
OL,18,Fincreasingly alarmed by the path the
OL,19,Freview has taken, the speed of
OL,20,Fprogress and the exclusion of families
OL,21,Ffrom the review process.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G3/15
