OL,7,F"Every single decision around the
OL,8,Freview which should have been taken in
OL,9,Fconsultation with families was taken
OL,10,Fby your organisation alone.
OL,12,F"No reasoning on the decisions taken
OL,13,Fhave been shared.
OL,15,F"Families have attempted to engage
OL,16,Fwith Swansea Bay University Health
OL,17,FBoard since the review's announcement
OL,18,Fin December 2023.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G4/15
