OL,5,Ccredibility'
OL,7,F"Repeated attempts to meet with your
OL,8,Fchief executive and wider executive
OL,9,Fteam have been dismissed out of hand.
OL,10,FMeeting invites were declined and
OL,11,Femails ignored.
OL,13,F"The appointment of Margaret Bowron KC
OL,14,Fby your predecessor as oversight chair
OL,15,Fon 31 January, without consultation
OL,16,Fwith families, was a disaster."
