OL,7,FMargaret Bowron KC had been appointed
OL,8,Fby the health board to oversee the
OL,9,Findependent review of maternity
OL,10,Fservices but resigned from the post in
OL,11,FJune after her presence became "an
OL,12,Funwelcome distraction from the work of
OL,13,Fthe review".
OL,15,FThe support group said the review is
OL,16,Fnow eight months behind schedule,
OL,17,Fadding: "Following all best practice,
OL,18,Fthis review should have been a co-
OL,19,Fproduction between us all. Instead it
OL,20,Fhas been the exact opposite."
