OL,7,FLlais, the official body representing
OL,8,Fpatient voices in Wales, has also
OL,9,Fwritten to the health board saying:
OL,10,F"You will recognise from recent
OL,11,Fcoverage and feedback from us that
OL,12,Fthere is a view that this review is
OL,13,Fnot sufficiently person/patient-
OL,14,Ffocused. Co-production and citizen
OL,15,Finvolvement must be at the centre of
OL,16,Fthis review.
