OL,7,FThe Swansea Bay Maternity Support
OL,8,FGroup is now calling for better
OL,9,Fprovision of mental health support for
OL,10,Fthe families involved in the review,
OL,11,Fadding: "In conclusion, as the group
OL,12,Fof people that should have been at the
OL,13,Fcentre of the review on day one we
OL,14,Fhave been let down, excluded and
OL,15,Ftreated with contempt. We have lost
OL,16,Fconfidence in the review that no
OL,17,Flonger has any credibility."
