OL,8,Fspokesperson for Swansea Bay
OL,9,FUniversity Health Board said: "We
OL,10,Funderstand the families' strength of
OL,11,Ffeeling, and we all want the same
OL,12,Foutcome ` to have a maternity and
OL,13,Fneonatal service which is the best it
OL,14,Fcan be.
