OL,7,F"More than 3,000 families each year
OL,8,Fdepend on our maternity services in
OL,9,FSwansea Bay, and we are working hard
OL,10,Fto continually improve them. The
OL,11,Frecent HIW report reflects the
OL,12,F'significant improvements' already
OL,13,Fmade, and we have firm actions in
OL,14,Fplace to complete outstanding work.
OL,16,F"We are committed to putting families,
OL,17,Fand staff, at the heart of the
OL,18,Findependent review; and we all want
OL,19,Fthe answers to the questions which the
OL,20,Freview will look into.
