OL,7,F"The review is now underway, with
OL,8,Fletters to be issued to families
OL,9,Fshortly inviting them to come forward
OL,10,Fto give their views. The review's
OL,11,Fwebsite will also launch next week;
OL,12,Fand a wider family and community
OL,13,Fvoices group is being set up to work
OL,14,Falongside it, with a dedicated email
OL,15,Fto collect views.
OL,17,F"In addition, Llais, the independent
OL,18,Fpatient advocate body for Wales, is
OL,19,Fsupporting the engagement work.
