OL,7,FMs Ockenden has said it is
OL,8,F"unbelievable" that bereaved and
OL,9,Fharmed families are having to campaign
OL,10,Ffor a review they feel they can trust.
OL,12,FThe Welsh Government previously
OL,13,Fresponded to Ms Ockenden's comments,
OL,14,Fsaying: "We will be seeking ongoing
OL,15,Fassurance that the health board is
OL,16,Fconstructively supporting the review
OL,17,Fprocess and robustly responding to any
OL,18,Femerging concerns and learning as a
OL,19,Fpriority.
